            <thetext>Suppose the following situation:

1. Start with a blank editor
2. Enter some text
3. Execute the &quot;Bold&quot; command at an empty selection at the end of the line
4. Hit &quot;Enter&quot; for a new paragraph

In IE users write bold text and e.g. with Firefox they write normal text. All browser should behave the same.

Additionally the &quot;cursorContext&quot; event should be regarded to return the correct values.</thetext>
